cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the challenges of managing and analyzing large amounts of data in the Industrial Internet, which falls under the domain of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also addresses issues related to security and privacy, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves the use of microservices, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
